<bibRefCitation id="EFB6CEFAFF94FF824DA9FB39FC68FB56" box="[663,903,1189,1214]" pageId="36" pageNumber="437" refId="ref37734" refString="Schulte II, J. A., Vindum, J. V., Win, H., Thin, T., Lwin, K. S. &amp; Shein, A. K. (2004) Phylogenetic relationships of the genus Ptyctolaemus (Squamata: Agamidae), with a description of a new species from Chin Hills of Western Myanmar. Proceedings of the California Academy of Sciences, 55, 222 - 247." type="journal article">
Schulte II 
